nodes.text: A waterworld, also known as water world, water-world, water planet, aquatic world, aquatic planet, ocean world, or ocean planet, was a type of planet covered primarily in water. Waterworlds in the galaxy included Kamino, Dac, Ando, Glee Anselm, Manaan, and Tion. The term "water world" also applied to aquatic moons such as Dorumaa. At some point in the distant past, inhabitants of ocean worlds operated lighthouses.
